  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix together bell peppers, sweet potato, eggplant, olive oil, vinegar, cumin, turmeric, cardamom, salt, and pepper.",
    "Transfer the mixture onto an oven-safe dish. Bake in preheated oven for 45 minutes or until vegetables are tender and golden brown on top.",
    "Remove from oven, let it cool slightly before serving as a sweet and flaky Indian vegetable crumble."
